In the face of turbulent national economy, raging global pandemic and other myriad of challenges Nigerians are facing, Supr. Ap. Pro. Samuel A. Usman, the Overseer, Eternal Sacred Order of the Cherubim & Seraphim Church, has assured the leaders and citizenry that there is no cause for alarm. According to him, God is set to restore the nation’s troubled economy. Usman emphasised that God has promised to intervene in the nation’s affairs, adding that it was time for liberation for the country, promising that total solution to the nation’s challenges would surely come. High Praises, Special Prayers At INL Annual Thanksgiving… CAN Debunks Dispute With LASG Over Archbishop’s Residence… The cleric made the declaration ahead of his church’s annual ‘Ark of Covenant Convention Celebration’, saying, there would be victory over challenges.